{"tid":608574,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"呆萌樹熊深夜光臨酒店 網民：要辦入住嗎？","createTime":"2018-03-28T09:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T15:51:32.000Z","uid":109136,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6d8f1801721e73076215fb89201dfddb93ba93de","tid":608574,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/australia/2018/03/20180326_AU_koala_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Faustralia%2F2018%2F03%2F20180326_AU_koala_01.jpg&h=5c70f18b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本月16日的深夜，一隻樹熊突然出現在了墨爾本東南部因沃洛什（Inverloch）的RACV海濱度假酒店的門口，牠默默地走到門前，抬手拍拍玻璃門，似乎是想要引起酒店工作人員的注意，讓他們幫忙開門入內。<br />\n<br />\n拍了一會兒後，這隻小傢伙好像是累了一般，一屁股地坐到地上開始休息起來，模樣十足可愛。酒店工作人員見狀也忍不住將此情此景拍下來，並分享在酒店的Facebook主頁上，瞬間吸引了一大批網民點讚和評論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/australia/2018/03/20180326_AU_koala_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Faustralia%2F2018%2F03%2F20180326_AU_koala_02.jpg&h=d2fff668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/australia/2018/03/20180326_AU_koala_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Faustralia%2F2018%2F03%2F20180326_AU_koala_03.jpg&h=1e55f6f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網友開玩笑地表示，這隻樹熊可能是想進門去喝一杯酒，「牠可能還想要辦理入住！誰來幫幫牠？！」酒店方面也靈機一觸，搞笑回復網民：「酒店房間被訂滿了！這位客官你就爬到門口的樹上休息去吧！」<br />\n<br />\n樹熊多以尤加利葉為主食，但挑剔的牠們在700多種尤加利樹中，只選擇其中的50種葉子來吃。由於飲食中沒有攝入太多能量，因此牠們每天能睡上20個小時。"},{"pid":"dac8ab754d4b7278a74b9ca9960453f44a996d1c","tid":608574,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82bdbbb53dc0e15d9e46bd015b8467ceb0db9d1","tid":608574,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a96fafc450e30a487e2d5d58ea607d1e21bdf4","tid":608574,"uid":146435,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/28/172841_8388620b55b9c0a2304173541e3b316f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F28%2F172841_8388620b55b9c0a2304173541e3b316f.png&h=68eaf568&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a01ff1e00b12bf1b7477e8d81883fea9c709927","tid":608574,"uid":7004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:29:15.000Z","msg":"好撚cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b488189f5ba8329760be753279336a55e0c6399","tid":608574,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a01ff1e00b12bf1b7477e8d81883fea9c709927","tid":608574,"uid":7004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:29:15.000Z","msg":"好撚cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:32:15.000Z","msg":"全世界最撚CUTE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a6973f1d322881ac784be77ac7fd28694de082","tid":608574,"uid":154871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:40:51.000Z","msg":"第二幅個樣好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfcbe99dbb1a6a3d3749cee59fe9b9c43fc9642","tid":608574,"uid":109136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"q